{"tid":1773894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"AV新片瓦斯爐掀討論 清水健、導演都朝聖留言 導演表示今後會加重瓦斯爐劇份","createTime":"2019-12-08T00:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T14:57:14.000Z","uid":133680,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ac13faad638bf8be14eb4548be51987707e6b68b","tid":1773894,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:19:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ebc.net.tw/News/Amp/188992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2FNews%2FAmp%2F188992&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRGCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=d0970fe8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ebc.net.tw/News/Amp/188992</a><br />\n<br />\n比女優搶戲！AV新片瓦斯爐掀討論 清水健、導演都朝聖留言<br />\n2019/12/07 10:05 東森新聞 責任編輯 陳俊宇<br />\n每個月老司機們最期待的，應該就是當月新番AV以及新人女優了！近日就有一部在 11 月剛發售的AV在網上引發討論，且焦點居然不在飾演人妻的新人女優辻井ほのか身上。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n▼新人女優辻井ほのか。（圖／辻井ほのか 推特）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本家電迷kebiyama時常在推特上分享各種型號的熱水器與瓦斯爐家電，甚至還會分析一些動漫作品中出現的家電，而平時讚數只有2位數的他，一則貼文突然爆紅。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n▼日本家電迷kebiyama的一則推文在網引發討論。（圖／kebiyama 推特）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nKebiyama貼出幾張11月時推出的新番AV「夫の目の前で他人にカラダを求めるHカップ超美人妻と濃厚不倫」總而言之就是人妻不倫片的截圖。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n指出劇中女優辻井穂香（辻井ほのか）與男優在廚房嘿嘿嘿的時候，發現了「National」國際牌的舊式嵌入式瓦斯爐，讓Kebiyama相當興奮，表示這種型號的瓦斯爐已經早早退出瓦斯行業界，卻意外地在AV中發現，可謂非常珍貴的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n大大&hellip;你褲子都脫了不看女優，反而看瓦斯爐...真的大丈夫&Sigma;(O_O)！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n這則貼文立即在推特引發話題，就連知名 AV 男優清水健也特來朝聖，並詢問 kebiyama 他們今天拍攝現場的舊瓦斯爐是什麼。對此Kebiyama也馬上回覆，還給出裝修的建議。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n▼AV界男優清水健也在底下回應。（圖／推特）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n此外作品的導演以及女優辻井穂香也來回應，導演表示「我們沒想到過在片場竟會藏有如此稀有的瓦斯爐，真的很開心知道這件事。今後，我會盡可能地在以後的作品讓瓦斯爐有更多角度入鏡。」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n▼辻井穂香則是覺得哭笑不得，「比起瓦斯爐拜託多看我好嘛！！」、「我會努力變得比瓦斯爐更性感的！」"},{"pid":"d22cafb4e9b406c2a329ce96c28f566af5e386e3","tid":1773894,"uid":39012,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"Hello 無圖 你想大家要圖定要老母？"},{"pid":"abd433e6646f8a28e8396b8da5bdf741dac67130","tid":1773894,"uid":42340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d22cafb4e9b406c2a329ce96c28f566af5e386e3","tid":1773894,"uid":39012,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"Hello 無圖 你想大家要圖定要老母？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:25:36.000Z","msg":"以為自己冇數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2d162b65bb2b5e216cb7fd879ba5529ed76220","tid":1773894,"uid":133680,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"d22cafb4e9b406c2a329ce96c28f566af5e386e3","tid":1773894,"uid":39012,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"Hello 無圖 你想大家要圖定要老母？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fqAaEji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfqAaEji.jpg&h=02251b6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f798835878b2a6af541917707d399bf4de4dbb7","tid":1773894,"uid":8216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:31:47.000Z","msg":"睇標題諗咩撚野煤氣爐，點知原黎係堅煤氣爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eba38049552a132995ab3e3a413ab12caaf61c1","tid":1773894,"uid":109701,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T00:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhy0g7i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhy0g7i.jpg&h=d04bc3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FifmL0E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFifmL0E.jpg&h=f246218b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cLqtdZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cLqtdZ.jpg&h=e050ca8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"